      "messageBody": "…xecution\n\nAdds the complete V16 outreach execution system on top of V15 Founder Autopilot:\n\n- outreach-execution/: 7 AR playbooks (batch, personalization, human review policy,\n  sector strategy, reply handling, call prep, objection follow-up, daily review)\n- scripts/: 9 new V16 scripts (readiness check, batch builder, personalizer,\n  human review queue, reply tracker, call prep builder, objection follow-up,\n  execution dashboard, daily run) + supporting outreach scripts\n- data/outreach/: seed data (prospect_batches, reviewed_messages, reply_tracker,\n  call_prep_queue, objection_followups) — synthetic, no PII\n- templates/outreach/: 7 AR draft templates (first touch, follow-ups, call prep)\n- frontend: sales-execution page, internal/outreach-command page, OutreachReviewCard\n- qa/: V16_OUTREACH_QA_CHECKLIST_AR.md\n- observability/: OUTREACH_OBSERVABILITY_PLAN_AR.md\n- ops/: V16_DAILY_SALES_EXECUTION_ROOM_AR.md\n- .github/workflows/: dealix-v16-real-outreach.yml (contents: read only)\n- Makefile: dealix-v16-readiness, dealix-v16-daily, dealix-outreach-dashboard targets\n- .gitignore: whitelist data/outreach/ alongside existing data/templates/\n\nAll V16 scripts enforce human-review-before-send: no automated external messages.\nReadiness check passes for 11 critical files. Daily run verified end-to-end.",
